data.description: Located just 5 minutes from Stone Mountain Park, this gorgeous split-level offers an excellent balance of modern additions, roomy living areas, and a huge backyard that's perfect for entertaining, relaxing, or spending time with the family.  Entire home has been freshly painted, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere. The recently renovated kitchen features beautiful granite countertops, stainless-steel appliances, and plenty of cabinet space. Unwind in the family room, which features a cozy fireplace and is a perfect retreat on chilly evenings.
